#### Quick Snippets
* Motors
    * FalconFX

        * type ```ctre::phoenix::motorcontrol::can::WPI_TalonFX *motor;```
        * call ```motor = new ctre::phoenix::motorcontrol::can::WPI_TalonFX(0);```
